The first time I heard someone say: &ldquo;Stack Safe Mutual Recursion using cats Eval DataType and Trampolining&rdquo; I figured I&rsquo;d found the ONE thing I wouldn&rsquo;t be able to write about, on the count of how complex it sounded.
